dates, comments, and private messaging.\r\n\r\nOne of Facebook\'s significant contributions to social interaction is its role in fostering community engagement. It enables users to join and create groups based on shared interests, hobbies, or affiliations, fostering discussions and connections beyond individual friendships. Additionally, Facebook Pages allow businesses, public figures, and organizations to establish a presence and interact with their audience.\r\n\r\nThe News Feed, a central feature of Facebook, curates content from friends, groups, and pages, providing users with a personalized stream of updates. The platform has also expanded its functionalities over the years, introducing features like Marketplace for buying and selling goods, Events for organizing and discovering local happenings, and fundraisers for supporting charitable causes.','javascript Swift HTML5 mysql','+ Front-end Developer : // Help with page layouts + Full Stack Developer : // Help with Django integration + Full Stack Developer : // Help with Django integration with DB + UI/UX Designer: // Help with User App Tools','2023-11-13 13:45:30','2023-11-16 04:00:49'),(4,3,'Netflix',' A popular streaming service for movies and TV shows, offering a vast library of content for subscribers.',10,1,'https://github.com/JaneDoe/TESTREPO','Founded in 1997 as a DVD-by-mail service, Netflix has evolved into a global streaming giant, fundamentally reshaping the way people consume entertainment. The platform offers a vast library of movies, TV shows, documentaries, and original content, accessible through a monthly subscription. Netflix\'s original productions, such as \"Stranger Things,\" \"The Crown,\" and \"Narcos,\" have garnered critical acclaim and a massive audience. The service employs algorithms to recommend personalized content based on users\' viewing history, enhancing the overall streaming experience. Netflix\'s on-demand model allows subscribers to binge-watch entire seasons, giving them unprecedented control over their entertainment choices. With its commitment to high-quality original programming and a user-friendly interface, Netflix has played a pivotal role in the rise of streaming as the dominant form of media consumption.','Rust linux apache mysql php','+ Front-end Developer : // Help with page layouts \r\n+ Full Stack Developer : // Help with Django integration \r\n+ Full Stack Developer : // Help with Django integration with DB \r\n+ UI/UX Designer: // Help with User App Tools','2023-11-13 13:47:47','2023-11-16 03:52:51'),(5,2,'Shazam','An app that identifies music by listening to a short sample, helping discover new songs and artists.',7,1,'https://github.com/JaneDoe/Shazam','Shazam, launched in 2002, is a music discovery app that has become a global sensation. The app\'s primary function is to identify songs, providing users with the artist, track name, and additional information by simply \"listening\" to a snippet of the audio. Shazam uses advanced audio fingerprinting technology, comparing the captured audio sample to its extensive database of millions of songs. Beyond identification, Shazam allows users to explore music, access lyrics, watch music videos, and connect to streaming services for an immersive music discovery experience. The app has become an essential tool for music enthusiasts, enabling them to instantly recognize and explore new songs and artists across genres.','Django MySQL Python Bootstrap Angularjs','+ Front-end Developer : // Help with page layouts + Full Stack Developer : // Help with Django integration + Full Stack Developer : // Help with Django integration with DB + UI/UX Designer: // Help with User App Tools','2023-11-13 15:19:43','2023-11-14 23:50:22'),(8,3,'WhatsApp','     A widely used messaging app that enables text, voice, and video communication globally.',11,1,'https://github.com/JimDoe/WhatsApp','Established in 2009, WhatsApp has become a ubiquitous messaging app that revolutionized real-time communication. Acquired by Facebook, it enables users to send text messages, make voice and video calls, and share multimedia content globally through the internet. Known for its simplicity and end-to-end encryption, WhatsApp prioritizes user privacy and security. Group chats allow users to connect with multiple friends simultaneously, fostering communication in various contexts. The app has transcended personal use, becoming an essential tool for businesses and organizations for both internal and customer communications. WhatsApp\'s cross-platform functionality, coupled with its commitment to a seamless and reliable messaging experience, has contributed to its widespread adoption as a primary means of staying connected in the digital age.','TypeScript Swift perl mongodb express vuejs nodejs','+ Front-end Developer : // Help with page layouts + Full Stack Developer : // Help with Django integration + Full Stack Developer : // Help with Django integration with DB + UI/UX Designer: // Help with User App Tools','2023-11-14 21:44:03','2023-11-16 03:54:09'),(9,9,'Pinterest','     A visual discovery and bookmarking platform where users discover and save ideas for various interests.',9,1,'https://github.com/MaxDoe/Pinterest','Launched in 2010, Pinterest is a unique visual discovery and bookmarking platform that allows users to explore and save ideas for various interests. Often described as a digital pinboard, users create themed boards and \'pin\' images or ideas related to topics like fashion, recipes, home decor, travel, and more. It serves as a virtual inspiration board where users curate content by saving pins from their own discoveries or from other users. Pinterest\'s intuitive interface encourages creativity and planning, making it a valuable tool for individuals seeking inspiration, DIY projects, or planning special events. The platform\'s visual-centric approach sets it apart, fostering a community of users who share and discover ideas through engaging visuals.','ruby postg